<h2>Rapid Descriptions</h2>
<div><div id='zzqdg2tsn8pom1kRiverRapidView88' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid364">Ankle Breaker</a></b> (Class 5.2)<br>
